HEADWORD: Pers
<hw>Pers</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[F. <ets>pers</ets>.]</ety> <def>Light blue; grayish blue; -- a term applied to different shades at different periods.</def> -- <def2><pos>n.</pos> <def>A cloth of sky-blue color.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark> ⟦ldquo⟧A long surcoat of <xex>pers</xex>.⟦rdquo⟧</def2>  <rj><au>Chaucer.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
